# GitLab command-line tool (glab).
#

{{- /*
GitLab personal access token for ~/.config/gitlab/token.
Resolved once via batched `op inject` in .chezmoi.toml.tmpl, then reused
from .secrets.gitlab_pat by all consumers.

Refresh after rotating the PAT in 1Password:  chezmoi apply --init

`private_` prefix → 0600 on Unix; no-op on Windows.

Defensive lookup via sprig's `dig`: empty when `.secrets` or the key is
missing (remote machines without `op`, or pre-[data.secrets] configs).
Empty rendered template → chezmoi skips writing ~/.config/gitlab/token.
*/ -}}
{{- with dig "secrets" "gitlab_pat" "" . -}}
{{ . }}
{{- end -}}
